{"tid":1618764,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"改咗 wifi hotspot 個名咁耐，今日終於有人留意到","createTime":"2019-10-04T06:28:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T07:35:07.000Z","uid":103325,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"546c8f1fe6085bb2cc4a649329d0046faedc4918","tid":1618764,"uid":103325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T06:28:33.000Z","msg":"話説今日搭巴士出去，都幾長途下，咪開個 wifi hotspot 俾另一部電話用，一部打機一部上網同聽歌啦<br />\n<br />\n架車本來好靜，車上邊個個唔係訓覺就係篤電話。直至去到某一個站，一個廢中上咗車&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n佢唔知發乜神經，架車行行下佢突然大聲呼喝：邊撚個黑警死全家呀<br />\n全車人都好撚奇怪嘅眼光望撚住佢(包括我)，不過佢講完呢句就靜咗，其他人亦無理佢，而我亦都係呢個時係至醒起一樣嘢&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n黑警死全家係我 wifi hotspot 個名<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1dM0xqa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1dM0xqa.png&h=4811e611&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n難得有人留意到，梗係要再撚下佢啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mHfkxqi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmHfkxqi.png&h=8df2708c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n隔咗一陣，佢又鳩叫：邊個屌我老母<br />\n<br />\n死廢中唔係咁撚廢呀，電話費都俾唔起，要係咁痴巴士 free wifi 用呀<br />\n再撚下你&hellip;<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VPXZNYP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVPXZNYP.png&h=55a29136&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過唔知佢見唔見到，因為無耐我就落車"},{"pid":"19ff6a5e91e1ffe25da36bff04a48ad34bc1c140","tid":1618764,"uid":139677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T06:29:23.000Z","msg":"笑撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"045a811f002d5b1e2fb94e301b2f61acca330473","tid":1618764,"uid":218158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T06:30:45.000Z","msg":"正到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b0bb3c80c2470c98853f001df8dbf5653823602","tid":1618764,"uid":301949,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T07:35:07.000Z","msg":"邊撚個黑警死全家呀<br />\n答：邊撚個黑警都死全家啦<br />\n<br />\n邊個屌我老母<br />\n答：你連邊個係你老豆都唔知？唔知就要問你老母你有幾多個老豆，你至少知你老母幾錢Q<br />\n<br />\n條IQ題好難答"}]}